<?xml version="1.0"?><?mso-application progid="Excel.Sheet"?><Workbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:x="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel" xmlns:ss="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:spreadsheet" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40"><DocumentProperties xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><LastAuthor>Djurre van Dijk</LastAuthor><Created>2019-05-06T09:40:07Z</Created><LastSaved>2019-05-06T09:40:07Z</LastSaved><Version>16.00</Version></DocumentProperties><OfficeDocumentSettings xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office"><AllowPNG/></OfficeDocumentSettings><ExcelWorkbook xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><WindowHeight>7620</WindowHeight><WindowWidth>21570</WindowWidth><WindowTopX>32767</WindowTopX><WindowTopY>32767</WindowTopY><RefModeR1C1/><ProtectStructure>False</ProtectStructure><ProtectWindows>False</ProtectWindows></ExcelWorkbook><Styles><Style ss:ID="Default" ss:Name="Normal"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Bottom"/><Borders/><Font ss:FontName="Calibri" x:Family="Swiss" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#000000"/><Interior/><NumberFormat/><Protection/></Style><Style ss:ID="s62"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/></Style><Style ss:ID="s63"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/><Interior/></Style><Style ss:ID="s64"><Alignment ss:Vertical="Top" ss:WrapText="1"/><Borders/><Font ss:FontName="Calibri" x:Family="Swiss" ss:Size="11" ss:Color="#000000"/></Style></Styles><Worksheet ss:Name="Script"><Table x:FullColumns="1" x:FullRows="1" ss:StyleID="s62" ss:DefaultColumnWidth="51.75" ss:DefaultRowHeight="15"><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="171.75"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="130.5"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="306.75"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="147.75"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="271.5"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:Width="120"/><Column ss:StyleID="s62" ss:AutoFitWidth="0" ss:Width="310.5"/><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UNIT_UPGRADES_FIREARMS</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">The DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES column contains info on what text between { } signs means (if applicable). It usually stands for either a numeric value, or a numeric value with an icon. Text between [ ] signs stands for a certain type of icon. </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SCENE ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TEXT ID</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE ENGLISH STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ALTERNATIVE LOCALIZED STRING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LOCALIZATION NOTES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEV TEAM / MISC NOTES</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSAULT_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Assault Rifle</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Karabin szturmowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ASSAULT_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire an Assault Rifle at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu z karabinu szturmowego.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SNIPER_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MX-2000 Sniper</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Snajperka MX-2000</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SNIPER_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a MX-2000 Rifle at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu z karabinu snajperskiego MX-2000.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GATLING_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gatling Gun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kartaczownica</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">GATLING_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a Gatling Gun at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ostrzelanie celu z kartaczownicy.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ELECTRIFIED_AMMO</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ammunition: Electrified</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Amunicja – porażająca</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ELECTRIFIED_AMMO</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Allows the unit to fire electrified ammunition to deal Arc damage and have a 12[StrengthWave/] chance (8[StrengthWave/] for repeating attacks) to inflict [abilityred]Electrified[/abilityred] to non-Ethereal units for 3[turn/].[br/][br/][productioncol]Only one kind of ammunition can be active at any time.[/productioncol]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Umożliwia jednostce strzelanie amunicją porażającą w celu zadawania obrażeń elektrycznych. Daje to szansę 12[StrengthWave/] (8[StrengthWave/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) spowodowania [abilityred]porażenia[/abilityred] u jednostek nieeterycznych na 3[turn/].[br/][br/][productioncol]W danej chwili można używać amunicji tylko jednego typu.[/productioncol]</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="8" ss:StyleID="s63"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FLECHETTE_AMMO</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ammunition: Flechette </Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Amunicja – strzałkowa </Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">FLECHETTE_AMMO</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Allows the unit to fire flechette ammunition, which has a 12[StrengthPhysical/] chance (8[StrengthPhysical/] for repeating attacks) to inflict [abilityred]Bleeding[/abilityred] on Cyborg and Biological units for 3[turn/].[br/][br/][productioncol]Only one kind of ammunition can be active at any time.[/productioncol]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Umożliwia jednostce strzelanie amunicją strzałkową z szansą 12[StrengthPhysical/] (8[StrengthPhysical/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) spowodowania [abilityred]krwawienia[/abilityred] u cyborgów i jednostek organicznych na 3[turn/].[br/][br/][productioncol]W danej chwili można używać amunicji tylko jednego typu.[/productioncol]</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="8" ss:StyleID="s63"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAIL_ACCELERATORS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rail Accelerators</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Akceleratory szynowe</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAIL_ACCELERATORS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Advanced accelerators built into the weapon stabilize the shot. Firearms attacks have {accuracyboost} accuracy and {rangeboost} extra range.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zaawansowane akceleratory wbudowane w broń stabilizują trajektorię pocisku, co zwiększa celność ataków bronią palną o {accuracyboost} i zapewnia {rangeboost} dodatkowego zasięgu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAIL_ACCELERATORS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MODIFIER_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{AccuracyBonus} accuracy and {RangeBonus} range.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{AccuracyBonus} do celności i {RangeBonus} do zasięgu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">INCENDIARY AMMO</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ammunition: Fire Burst</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Amunicja – zapalająca wybuchowa</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="75"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">INCENDIARY AMMO</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Allows the unit to fire incendiary ammunition to deal Thermal damage and have a 12[StrengthThermal/] chance (8[StrengthThermal/] for repeating attacks) to set non-Ethereal and non-Mineral targets on fire, causing [abilityred]Burning[/abilityred] for 3[turn/].[br/][br/]Attacks deal 75% of their damage to adjacent units.[br/][br/][productioncol]Only one kind of ammunition can be active at any time.[/productioncol]</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Umożliwia jednostce strzelanie amunicją zapalającą, która zadaje obrażenia cieplne i ma szansę 12[StrengthThermal/] (8[StrengthThermal/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) podpalenia celu nieeterycznego i niemineralnego, co powoduje [abilityred]oparzenie[/abilityred] na 3[turn/].[br/][br/]Ataki zadają 75% pkt. obrażeń sąsiadującym jednostkom.[br/][br/][productioncol]W danej chwili można używać amunicji tylko jednego typu.[/productioncol]</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="8" ss:StyleID="s63"/></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TRICORIUM_SHOCKWAVE_ROUNDS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Shockwave Infuser</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Infuzor uderzeniowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="90"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TRICORIUM_SHOCKWAVE_ROUNDS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Firearms attacks have a {StrengthSingle}[StrengthPhysical/] strength chance ({ChanceRepeat}[StrengthPhysical/] for repeating attacks) to cause [abilityred]Concussion[/abilityred] for {duration}[turn/] on the primary target while [abilityred]Staggering[/abilityred] adjacent units with High Impact.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Atak bronią palną ma szansę (siła {StrengthSingle}[StrengthPhysical/], {ChanceRepeat}[StrengthPhysical/] dla ataków wielokrotnych) spowodowania [abilityred]wstrząsu[/abilityred] na {duration}[turn/] u głównego celu i [abilityred]zachwiania[/abilityred] u jednostek sąsiadujących wskutek silnego uderzenia.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SHOTGUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Shotgun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzelba</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SHOTGUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a Shotgun at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Oddaje strzał do celu przy użyciu strzelby.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PISTOL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pistol</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pistolet</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PISTOL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a Pistol at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu z pistoletu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AIRCRAFT_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Aircraft Gun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Karabin lotniczy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AIRCRAFT_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A powerful machine gun for an aircraft</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Potężny karabin maszynowy dla lotnictwa.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BASIC_PISTOL_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pistol</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pistolet</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BASIC_ASSAULT_RIFLE_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Assault Rifle</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Karabin szturmowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BASIC_SNIPER_RIFLE_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MX-2000 Sniper</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Snajperka MX-2000</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BASIC_ROTARY_CANNON</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rotary Cannon</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działo obrotowe</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BASIC_SHOT_GUN_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Shotgun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzelba</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EQUIPMENT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BASIC_VORPAL_SNIPER_RIFLE</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vorpal Sniper Rifle</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Karabin snajperski rozpadu</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEFENSE_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Defense Gun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działko obronne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DEFENSE_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire the Defense Gun at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu z działka obronnego.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAIL_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Railgun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działko magnetyczne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAIL_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fires the Railgun at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu z działka magnetycznego.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAIL_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gives the unit a Rail Gun.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Daje jednostce działko magnetyczne.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POWER_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Vorpal Shot</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pocisk rozpadu</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POWER_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire the Vorpal Sniper rifle at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu z karabinu snajperskiego rozpadu.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POWER_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EFFECT_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Power Shot</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pocisk wzmocniony</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">POWER_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">EFFECT_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{PowerShotCritChance} critical chance.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">{PowerShotCritChance} szansy na trafienie krytyczne.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OVERPOWERING_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Concussive Shot</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pocisk wstrząsowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">OVERPOWERING_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire an overpowering shot, intending to stun the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela pociskiem obezwładniającym, próbując oszołomić cel.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLINDING_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Blinding Snap Shot</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pocisk oślepiający</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">BLINDING_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">A quick shot that fires a blinding flash round.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Szybki strzał oślepiającym pociskiem błyskowym.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISASSEMBLER_SHELL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Disassembler Shot</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pocisk demontujący</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DISASSEMBLER_SHELL</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a Disassembler Shot at the ground with 1 hex radius area of effect.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela w ziemię pociskiem demontującym, który ma obszar rażenia o promieniu 2 pól.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TOXIN_NANITES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Toxin Nanites Ammunition</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Toksyczna amunicja nanitowa</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="90"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">TOXIN_NANITES</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Replaces the Disassembler shell with a Toxic variant. It now leaves behind a cloud of Toxic Nanites that deal {ToxinHazardDamage} damage to enemy units standing in it, as well as having a {ToxicHazardChance} strength chance to apply [abilityred]Debilitating Infection[/abilityred] to Biological or Cyborg units.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Zastępuje pocisk demontujący wariantem toksycznym. Pozostawia chmurę zatruwających nanitów, zadającą {ToxinHazardDamage} pkt. obrażeń stojącym w niej wrogim jednostkom i mającą szansę ({ToxicHazardChance} siły) na wywołanie [abilityred]infekcji osłabiającej[/abilityred] u jednostek organicznych i cyborgów.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAVAL_RAILGUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Naval Railgun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Okrętowe działko magnetyczne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAVAL_RAILGUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a ship mounted Railgun at the target unit.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do wskazanej jednostki z działka magnetycznego zamontowanego na okręcie.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WRECKING_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wrecking Shot</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pocisk rozbiórkowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">WRECKING_SHOT</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a wrecking shot at the target.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu pociskiem rozbiórkowym.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAVAL_CANNON</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Naval Cannon</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działo okrętowe</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAVAL_CANNON</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a ship mounted Cannon at the target unit.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do wskazanej jednostki z działa zamontowanego na okręcie.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LARGE_CALIBER_WEAPONS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kinetic Phase Modulator</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Kinetyczny modulator fazowy</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LARGE_CALIBER_WEAPONS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UPGRADE_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Upgrades Firearms so that rounds travel in a modified dimensional phase, allowing them to bypass {ShieldBypass}[shield/] and ignore {LoSIgnore}% of the accuracy penalties from line of sight and units in the way.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Ulepsza broń palną w taki sposób, że pociski przechodzą przez fazę pozawymiarową, dzięki czemu omijają {ShieldBypass}[shield/] i ignorują {LoSIgnore}% kar do celności od linii widzenia i zasłaniających jednostek.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">LARGE_CALIBER_WEAPONS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">MOD_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bypass {ShieldBypass} and ignore {LoSIgnore}% of line of sight and unit in the way penalties.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Omija {ShieldBypass} i ignoruje {LoSIgnore}% kar wynikających z linii widzenia i zasłaniających jednostek.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SPIKE_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Spike Gun</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działko igłowe</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SPIKE_GUN</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Fire a Spike Gun at the target. Damage increases by {DamageIncrease} when unit stands within a Trench.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Strzela do celu z działka igłowego. Obrażenia są większe o {DamageIncrease}, gdy jednostka znajduje się w okopie.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AUTOCANNONS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Autocannons</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Działa automatyczne</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">AUTOCANNONS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">ABILITY_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="S